    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom-quality condition and represents the pinnacle of its model. It has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, with every mechanical component functioning flawlessly and the exterior paint and interior upholstery showing zero signs of wear. All original features are intact, and the engine performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine example that requires absolutely no work or attention.",
