    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally maintained vehicle, representing a premier choice for those seeking reliability and refined performance. This automobile has been subject to a rigorous multi-point inspection, ensuring all mechanical systems operate at peak efficiency. The interior remains in superior condition, complemented by a well-preserved exterior that reflects a history of diligent care. This offering represents a sophisticated investment for the discerning driver who values both substance and style.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
