      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it a perfect pick if you're looking for something reliable and ready for the road. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love for it to go to a good home. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six. This unit is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a 3.62 ratio limited-slip differential. Mechanical highlights include a comprehensive VANOS overhaul with Beisan components, rod bearing replacement with VAC treated shells, and a structural subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry is enhanced via Bilstein PSS10 coilovers, providing adjustable rebound and compression for precise cornering loads. Engine health is verified by recent valve lash adjustments and consistent oil analysis. While the chassis shows minor aesthetic wear consistent with its mileage, the powertrain delivers linear torque and the signature metallic rasp of individual throttle bodies with absolute precision. A mechanically sorted specimen for the purist who demands peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used car for sale. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. No mechanical issues. Ready for immediate pickup.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior finish retains a high-gloss luster, complemented by clean alloy wheels and tires with plenty of tread remaining. While there are a few minor, superficial stone chips on the leading edge of the hood from highway driving, the body remains straight and free of major dents. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, and the dashboard remains crack-free. Every feature, including the dual-zone climate control, premium audio system, and heated seats, has been tested and works perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has benefited from synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. We have recently performed a comprehensive multi-point inspection and replaced the brake pads to ensure the next owner has total peace of mind. This is a reliable, well-cared-for example that performs beautifully on the road.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
